Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.56,0:00:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風在說著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.87,0:00:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃 太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.85,0:00:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奢華糕點 百萬石饅頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.85,0:00:08.25,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}這裡惡搞琦玉名點「十萬石饅頭」的CM
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.26,0:00:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要整理一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.33,0:00:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼芽間會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.96,0:00:16.13,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}超強怨念 被虐殺婆婆的怨靈襲向無情義的兒媳！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為世上還有心願未了所以不能成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.98,0:00:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…這個想法是比較合理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.07,0:00:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.40,0:00:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 我所認識的芽間不管何時…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是微笑著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會喜歡這種醜八怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都想向芽間道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.75,0:00:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不止是低頭認錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.48,0:00:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點事情我還是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 說不定這也是芽間的願望哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.60,0:01:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望仁碳去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校…

Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.65,0:02:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 怎麼突然想去上學了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.51,0:02:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啥 就是想去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉強自己比較好噢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什麼意思啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.58,0:03:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明之前還是你叫我去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前是之前…向前看齊～！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.95,0:03:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是仁碳的表情好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刷得一乾二淨！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁…碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也依靠一下我吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓你成佛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳的媽媽已經成佛了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成佛…到底是怎麼一回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常心 平常心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我心中一切皆無 無 無
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然一臉沒事的樣子來學校了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的是那誰吧 一年三班的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對 安城鳴子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.09,0:04:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:12.00,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我都說了 果然是那樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:12.99,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}就說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 安城？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就叫做大失所望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也有幾個人注意到我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一直沒來的那傢伙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 還被校長叫過去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疏忽大意了吧 鳴子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love Hotel什麼的其實沒什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城完勝了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成這樣的話 之前拚命做的準備都白費了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.08,0:05:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說被PTA的人看到了呢 男的還是個大叔的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:49.11,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}PTA: Parent-Teacher Association 家長教師協會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援交？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 大家回到座位上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城你也趕快回到座位上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 請大家翻開課本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失策了啊 鳴子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個故事中說的「我」的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有著這樣幾種憤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先第一種是 對「他」和「妻子」的背叛感到的憤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時候安城還做筆記啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:44.47,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}身為和丈夫親密無間的摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:47.41,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}卻給「我」深愛的妻子寫了信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:55.59,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}其次 懷有共同秘密的二人在信中使用了密碼進行交流
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙從小時候開始就這樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦子不好 掌握不好要領
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嘛 安城
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不好拜託她的話我們也可以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:59.62,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}「我」作為男人的自尊心嚴重受創
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:00.67,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\frz219.944\pos(1090,404)}不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:00.67,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(782,291)\frz217.875}根本沒做！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:00.67,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(672,353)\frz217.875}！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:01.90,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1028,179)\frz327.529}別胡說了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:01.90,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz327.529\pos(1119,266)}！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:01.90,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz327.529\pos(1111,290)}！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:01.90,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz326.706\pos(562,212)}給我永遠閉上嘴吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:01.90,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz326.706\pos(747,359)}！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:01.90,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz329.486\pos(361,383)}去死！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:01.90,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz329.486\pos(401,431)}！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後第二種是對自己的憤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:06.70,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(1038,425,1071,431)\frz106.17}別擅自認定！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:06.70,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz99.371\move(636,255,669,261)}救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了信的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓「他」看到自己作為男人 作為丈夫的優越性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我」交給了妻子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援交？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是個大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也可以呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援交 援交…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.73,0:07:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是那麼久都沒來學校的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有入學指導…最開始的一周來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:08:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 這臉很少見吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…你是…宿海君？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙你們不是何時何地都能見著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LovHo？ 這種事情值得鬧那麼大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:13.96,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}LovHo: Love Hotel的簡稱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙不管怎麼看 都像是去過LovHo好幾次的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.82,0:08:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…的LovHo臉吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.21,0:08:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這傢伙 是絕對不會搞援交的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這傢伙還是A型血 山羊座 和冒險無緣的正經相
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴眼鏡總板著臉愛惜物品喜歡收拾整理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.55,0:08:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小開始就喜歡收集各種小東西 戴著眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.24,0:08:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是無聊到死的女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.69,0:08:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說那麼多廢話！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 拿上書包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一…下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然喊「看著我吧」 不管怎麼想都是變態吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你替我出頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我決不是LovHo臉！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒去LovHo嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒進去過！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「好了好了」那算什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 總之先回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽也在擔心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校肯定已經跟家裡聯繫過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對會被罵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人絕對不會原諒這種事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 安城
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…也不能這樣啊…

Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:06.04,title_no,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(692,555)}第六集
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:06.04,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(656,638)}忘記 別忘記

Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 說什麼要在這裡住 安鳴你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要等這陣風過去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這陣風…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可是凝聚了我的汗水淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他各種男汁的我的城堡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是大家一起建的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是證據啊 看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刻上去的哈姆太郎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈姆太郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說是火腿 不如說是香腸？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:31.05,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}哈姆和火腿同音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.07,0:10:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 你那男汁太臭了 要打掃乾淨再說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.81,0:10:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等等下 別碰那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.06,0:10:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 這是啥！都腐爛了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊 那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算說要住下來 不跟老媽說一聲的話還是有問題的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情會鬧得更大的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她膽子小嘛 總是藏在芽間的身後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:10:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在芽間人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 要去芽間家裡看看嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不準可以找出什麼實現芽間願望的提示
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你幫我 實現我的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啥 只是想帶上芽間一起去比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 她在的話 說「去芽間家裡」什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得不太合適嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.87,0:11:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然意外地會做人呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.89,0:11:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 我畢竟在越南獲得了薩滿五級的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那種東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.71,0:11:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 這樣定了的話 也給雪集他們發郵件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…地址地址
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:54.28,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz5.826\pos(519,551)}快定期測驗了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:54.28,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz5.826\pos(631,583)}今天會很晚放學所以去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:54.28,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz5.826\pos(531,644)}鶴見也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 這麼冷酷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重點高中就是那樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.13,0:12:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 本來我還在想 大家那麼久沒見 居然都沒變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不可能的啊 一點點地在變著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 還是不要去芽間家裡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們本來就沒有去芽間家裡玩過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…因為芽間她爸很可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 說不定是個好機會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 我也想給芽間燒燒香什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去了的話 芽間的媽媽會是什麼表情呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.14,0:12:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信 大家居然都來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣子肯定也會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 進來進來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去和芽衣子打個招呼怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在動搖什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情我本來就清楚的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是芽衣子的房間 請進
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.66,0:13:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 鶴見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美奈子想讓你把這個交給松雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正同一個班 自己交給他就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 鶴見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.16,0:14:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為一直在他身邊就比我們強嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.04,0:14:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見你喜歡松雪君的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說啥呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回去了嗎？ 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近這附近有奇怪的傢伙出沒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是像那樣被人妒忌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的女裝照片發過去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.78,0:14:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不好一下子就能解決這煩惱了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來宿海他們 好像要去芽間家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.79,0:15:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都把宿海說的話當真了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明大家都沒辦法真的把過去當作過去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.84,0:15:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以松雪集這個人為首呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不否定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變老實了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你面前的話 不管怎麼解釋都沒用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人不爽 那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是高中水平 還是這樣那樣的條件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明現在都是我比他高出許多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是和那時候一樣 被那傢伙隨意擺佈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在居然連芽間的名字都用上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底要把別人玩弄到什麼地步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是他說要到秘密基地集合…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:16:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天…好像是芽間提出來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.90,0:16:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 對 被芽間打電話叫出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.43,0:16:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了 那天 她好像說要商量什麼事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間說有事要和大家商量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間的日記 居然這麼容易就借到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個好媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.51,0:16:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是太冷清了 房間弄成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她爸爸說 不能一直被芽衣子所束縛著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就把這間屋子收拾了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…芽衣子的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果看到原本的房間 會更痛苦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果看到…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做媽媽的心情 我是不太理解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過她肯定把自己孩子的一切 看得比什麼都要重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也會說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是先回家一趟好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.79,0:17:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才不是怕家裡人擔心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.64,0:17:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想起有些事情必須要做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不老實
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 日記拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去秘密基地慢慢研讀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…可以等下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.93,0:17:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 今天該我做晚飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.19,0:17:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且早上的盤子都還沒洗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先讀了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我不在的時候先不要看 絕對不要看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.27,0:17:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我一個了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.18,0:17:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了反而更痛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:18:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 看不到反而更好嗎 芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:16.86,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}仁碳 歡迎回來 學上得怎樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了…反而更…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.77,0:18:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢…就隨他們一起去了 見到了你媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒收！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒收！沒收！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒收！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做的話 媽媽又要想起芽間的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓媽媽很寂寞很寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不想再讓媽媽更寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再讓媽媽想起我的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想讓她想起來什麼的 是不可能的吧？ 畢竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算那麼一點都好…也希望媽媽能把我忘掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說謊了 你不是說了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家沒把你忘了讓你很高興什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧你！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.37,0:19:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是這樣只考慮別人的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多考慮一下自己的事情啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人不爽啊 你那態度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.19,0:19:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明很難過 卻還強顏歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭的都是為別人而哭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…我會這麼憤怒？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.41,0:19:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:19:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:19:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻血！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.54,0:20:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.34,0:20:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 快塞紙巾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.28,0:20:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紙巾！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後仰頭躺著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話慢慢就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時間？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.41,0:20:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在幹什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我在幹什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.13,0:20:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？ 都這個時間了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你才是 不是回家了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.09,0:21:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你那樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.98,0:21:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的 這是剛才殘留下來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是對你有什麼非分之想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.06,0:21:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢材！變態！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.26,0:21:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H！Sketch！One touch！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.26,0:21:13.19,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}N年前流行於日本的一句押韻文 用來形容變態的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯的…那傢伙絕對是處女…

Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.81,0:23:01.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.58,0:21:35.30,ed_jp_formal_A,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}出会いは　ふっとした　瞬間　帰り道の交差点で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:41.27,ed_jp_formal_A,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}声をかけてくれたね　「一緒に帰ろう」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:49.86,ed_jp_formal_A,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}あぁ　花火が夜空　きれいに咲いて　ちょっとセツナク
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.07,0:21:56.11,ed_jp_formal_A,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}あぁ　風が時間とともに　流れる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:22:00.28,ed_jp_formal_A,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,0)}嬉しくって　楽しくって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:03.87,ed_jp_formal_A,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,0)}冒険も　いろいろしたね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.99,0:22:10.66,ed_jp_formal_A,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}二人の　秘密の　基地の中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.86,0:22:11.64,ed_jp_formal_A,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,0)}君と夏の終わり　将来の夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:15.00,ed_jp_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,200)}君と夏の終わり　将来の夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:18.17,ed_jp_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,0)}大きな希望　忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.17,0:22:25.10,ed_jp_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}10年後の8月　また出会えるのを　信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.26,0:22:28.55,ed_jp_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,0)}君が最後まで　心から
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.56,0:22:32.39,ed_jp_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,200)}「ありがとう」叫んでいたこと　知ってたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.39,0:22:39.44,ed_jp_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}涙をこらえて　笑顔でさようなら　せつないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.78,0:22:48.95,ed_jp_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}最高の想い出を...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.58,0:21:35.30,ed_cn_formal_A,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}相遇就在不經意的瞬間  站在歸途的交叉路口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:41.27,ed_cn_formal_A,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}你叫住了我 說了聲「一起回去吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:49.86,ed_cn_formal_A,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}啊 煙花在夜空中 絢爛地綻放 卻讓人有些失落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.07,0:21:56.11,ed_cn_formal_A,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}啊 風隨著時間 一同流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:22:00.28,ed_cn_formal_A,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,0)}好興奮 好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:03.87,ed_cn_formal_A,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,0)}還記得那無數次的冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.99,0:22:10.66,ed_cn_formal_A,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}就在我們兩人的秘密基地裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.86,0:22:11.64,ed_cn_formal_A,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,0)}在夏天的尾聲 和你暢談未來的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:15.00,ed_cn_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,200)}在夏天的尾聲 和你暢談未來的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:18.17,ed_cn_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,0)}一同許下的那個大大的願望 又怎能遺忘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.17,0:22:25.10,ed_cn_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}堅信著 10年後的8月 還會與你重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.26,0:22:28.55,ed_cn_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,0)}我知道 直到分別前的最後一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.56,0:22:32.39,ed_cn_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,200)}你仍真心呼喊著說「謝謝」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.39,0:22:39.44,ed_cn_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}我知道 忍住淚水微笑著說再見 有多心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.78,0:22:48.95,ed_cn_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}那份最難忘的回憶…
